7 Treasurer may issue Article XI-Q bonds in an amount not to exceed $19 million of net proceeds for
8 the purposes specified in subsection [(3)] (6) of this section, plus an amount estimated by the State
9 Treasurer to pay estimated bond-related costs.
10 (2)[(a)] Bonds may not be issued pursuant to this section or section 10, chapter 685, Oregon
