43 project under ORS 1.181 (3) or a courthouse improvement project under ORS 1.181 (4) may
44 include a requirement that the county transfer to the Oregon Courthouse Capital Construction and
45 Improvement Fund an amount not less than 50 percent of the total estimated costs of a project
